<div id="v490.10.16"><span class="G191 s">He that heareth</span><span class="G5216 s"> you</span><span class="G191 s"> heareth</span><span class="G1700 s"> me</span><span class="G2532 s">; and</span><span class="G114 s"> he that despiseth</span><span class="G5209 s"> you</span><span class="G114 s"> despiseth</span><span class="G1691 s"> me</span><span class="G1161 s">; and</span><span class="G114 s"> he that despiseth</span><span class="G1691 s"> me</span><span class="G114 s"> despiseth</span><span class="G649 s"> him that sent</span><span class="G3165 s"> me</span>.</div>
